qas.question: Nền kinh tế của Utrecht phụ thuộc vào điều gì

answers.text: The economy of Utrecht depends for a large part on the several large institutions located in the city

qas.question: những gì là trung tâm ở Utrecht

answers.text: It is the centre of the Dutch railroad network and the location of the head office of Nederlandse Spoorwegen

qas.question: Ngân hàng có trụ sở chính ở Utrecht

answers.text: Rabobank, a large bank, has its headquarters in Utrecht.
